    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2394530/extras/8a3fa56199601fdbd23a6f68b0e4e981.avif?t=1706712854\" width=600 height=100 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Dethrone the King. Simple as that</strong></h2><br>Immerse yourself in a serene and fascinating world where every move counts. <br><br>As you progress through beautifully designed puzzles, you will encounter challenging scenarios that require strategic thinking and careful planning.<br><br>Move across the board, defeat enemy pawns and clear your way to the King!<br><br><strong>Checkmate!</strong><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2394530/extras/Gif1.gif?t=1706712854\" /></span><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2394530/extras/eb5516449ec8b14ce67c21bd2c4e132f.avif?t=1706712854\" width=600 height=100 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>One pawn to rule them all</strong></h2><br>Change your form and become any other chess piece, acquiring their moveset. <br><br>Will you choose the agile mobility of a Knight or the imposing strength of a Rook?<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2394530/extras/Gif2.gif?t=1706712854\" /></span><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2394530/extras/9da3349abe475229e55dbb0a7ec27fcd.poster.avif?t=1706712854\" width=600 height=100 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2394530/extras/9da3349abe475229e55dbb0a7ec27fcd.webm?t=1706712854\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2394530/extras/9da3349abe475229e55dbb0a7ec27fcd.mp4?t=1706712854\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>An uncommon board</strong></h2><br>Special tiles can be both a blessing or a curse. <br><br>Teleport, block the enemies, create new paths and unleash your creativity as you adapt to ever-changing circumstances.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2394530/extras/Gif3.gif?t=1706712854\" /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Features:</strong></h2><br> <ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>80+ hand-crafted levels</strong></li></ul><br> <ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Control one single pawn</strong> in this <strong>original and relaxing gameplay</strong> </li></ul><br> <ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Unique mechanic</strong> for each world</li></ul><br> <ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>No chess knowledge needed</strong>, for both seasoned chess players and newcomers!</li></ul> <br> <ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Originally</strong> composed soundtrack</li></ul>",
